#Clustering Jerarquico
train3_dist <- dist(train3)
hc <- hclust(train3_dist, method = "ward.D2")
plot(hc, cex=0.5, axes=FALSE)
rect.hclust(hc, k=3)

fviz_dend(hc, k=3, rect = TRUE, cex = 0.5)

groups <- cutree(hc, k=3)
